Assertion is to check the condition without using SYSOUT statements 
Assertion can be implemented in three types
1. asser(i=10); // It simply check the condition if its true it will execute else it will hault programm by throwing Assertion exception
2. assert(i=10):"Message to be display" //If its fails and throw error wit will come with message provided
3. assert(i=10): text() //we can also include some method where it perforn action mention in text() method  